Function: digits
Section: conversions
C-Name: digits
Prototype: GDG
Help: digits(x,{b=10}): gives the vector formed by the digits of x in base b (x and b
 integers).
Doc:
 outputs the vector of the digits of $|x|$ in base $b$, where $x$ and $b$ are integers.
 See \kbd{fromdigits} for the reverse operation.
